Configuration dialog and uninstall one of the previous versions of AJDT feature

"apply changes" option in a confirmation dialog that does not require restart.
Then when download finished I've got an error popup with text "An error has
occured. See error log for details." Another error dialog with the list is in
background, but I can't get to it because first modal popup reappear again and
again when I click OK button.
